\cf2 Fundraising for charitable purposes is a very difficult process. Fundraising must first be approved by the Department for Islamic Affairs and Charitable Activities (IACAD), otherwise, fundraising violates the UAE Income Tax Act. This can lead to imprisonment, fines ranging from $ 68 thousand to $ 136 thousand and even deportation.\
\
