\f1 \cf3 \cb4 \strokec3 With the frequent sandstorms in the UAE, you would think you\'92d be forgiven for having a dusty car. However, dirty cars are seen to be \'93disfiguring the city image and public health\'94. As a result, they are routinely towed away, with owners being slapped with fines and impound fees of 3,000 dirhams
