Photographing in the United Arab Emirates is generally dangerous. Apart from the fact that photographing military buildings, courts and buildings are prohibited, it is also strictly forbidden to take a photo of an accident even aviation accidents. The penalty for this is from 50,000 to 3,000,000 and deportation.\
